DML is used to manage and manipulate the actual data stored within the structures created by DDL. 
If DDL builds the house, DML is the furniture inside

INSERT: Adds new rows of data into a table.
UPDATE: Modifies existing data values.
DELETE: Removes specific rows based on conditions.
SELECT: Retrieves or reads data 

